WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.027 --> 00:00:02.223
<v ->I don't know about you,</v>

2
00:00:02.223 --> 00:00:05.091
but movies about everyday heroes make me cry.

3
00:00:05.091 --> 00:00:07.529
If a movie were made about the life of Judy Wicks,

4
00:00:07.529 --> 00:00:09.293
I would certainly be crying.

5
00:00:09.293 --> 00:00:12.603
This woman is a testament to what one person can do

6
00:00:12.603 --> 00:00:15.203
fueled by a social conscience and passion.

7
00:00:15.203 --> 00:00:17.347
As a conscientious cafe owner,

8
00:00:17.347 --> 00:00:19.493
Judy began seeing the interrelationship

9
00:00:19.493 --> 00:00:21.902
between everything she served in her restaurant

10
00:00:21.902 --> 00:00:23.632
and went to the ends of the earth to see

11
00:00:23.632 --> 00:00:25.234
the political ramifications

12
00:00:25.234 --> 00:00:28.055
of supporting certain commodity industries.

13
00:00:28.055 --> 00:00:30.644
She ultimately met with the Zapatistas in Mexico

14
00:00:30.644 --> 00:00:33.489
in an activist program she humorously called

15
00:00:33.489 --> 00:00:35.538
"Eating with the Enemy."

16
